# {{ profile.title }}

## 氏名・基本情報

| 項目 | 内容 |
|---|---|
| 氏名 | {{ profile.name }} |
| 現在の職種 | {{ profile.basic_info.current_role }} |
| 経験 | {{ profile.basic_info.experience }} |
| 希望職種 | {{ profile.basic_info.desired_role }} |
| 居住地・勤務可能エリア | {{ profile.basic_info.location }} |

## 職務要約

{{ profile.summary }}

## 活かせる経験・知識・技術

{% for item in profile.strengths %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

## 技術スタック

<div class="skill-grid">
{% for skill in skills %}
  <section class="skill-card">
    <h3>{{ skill.category }}</h3>
    <div class="tag-list">
{% for item in skill["items"] %}
      <span class="tag">{{ item }}</span>
{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
{% endfor %}
</div>

## AI活用経験

<div class="ai-usage-list">
{% for item in profile.ai_usage %}
  <div class="ai-usage-item">
    <span class="ai-label">活用</span>
    <span>{{ item }}</span>
  </div>
{% endfor %}
</div>

## プロジェクト経歴

{% for project in projects %}
<div class="project">

### {{ project.name }}

<table class="project-summary-table">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <th>期間</th>
      <td>{{ project.period.from }}〜{{ project.period.to }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>役割</th>
      <td>{{ project.role }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>チーム規模</th>
      <td>{{ project.team_size }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>概要</th>
      <td>{{ project.summary }}</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<section class="project-section">
<h4>担当業務</h4>

<ul>
{% for item in project.responsibilities %}
  <li>{{ item }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
</section>

<section class="project-section">
<h4>成果・改善</h4>

<ul>
{% for item in project.achievements %}
  <li>{{ item }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
</section>

<section class="project-section">
<h4>開発環境</h4>

<table class="env-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>区分</th>
      <th>技術</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>言語</td>
      <td>{{ project.technologies.languages | join(", ") }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>FW/ライブラリ</td>
      <td>{{ project.technologies.frameworks | join(", ") }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>DB</td>
      <td>{{ project.technologies.db | join(", ") }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>ツール</td>
      <td>{{ project.technologies.tools | join(", ") }}</td>
    </tr>
{% if project.versions %}
    <tr class="version-row">
      <td>バージョン</td>
      <td>{{ project.versions | join(", ") }}</td>
    </tr>
{% endif %}
    <tr class="ai-env-row">
      <td>AI活用</td>
      <td>{{ project.ai_usage | select_enabled | join(", ") }}</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
</section>

<section class="project-section">
<h4>担当工程</h4>

<table class="phase-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>要件定義</th>
      <th>基本設計</th>
      <th>詳細設計</th>
      <th>実装</th>
      <th>レビュー</th>
      <th>テスト</th>
      <th>運用保守</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>{% if project.phases.requirement %}<span class="phase-dot"></span>{% endif %}</td>
      <td>{% if project.phases.basic_design %}<span class="phase-dot"></span>{% endif %}</td>
      <td>{% if project.phases.detail_design %}<span class="phase-dot"></span>{% endif %}</td>
      <td>{% if project.phases.implementation %}<span class="phase-dot"></span>{% endif %}</td>
      <td>{% if project.phases.review %}<span class="phase-dot"></span>{% endif %}</td>
      <td>{% if project.phases.test %}<span class="phase-dot"></span>{% endif %}</td>
      <td>{% if project.phases.operation %}<span class="phase-dot"></span>{% endif %}</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
</section>

</div>

{% endfor %}
